data.description: New roof just installed! Come see this cute-as-a-button home with a great layout! Lots of living space, with both a living room and family room that's open to the kitchen. Stainless steel appliances, solid countertops, and lots of storage. New flooring in all 3 bedrooms! Spacious primary bedroom with plenty of closet space and large walk-in shower. New paint inside and out.  New washer and dryer. Screened porch provides an ideal space to enjoy your morning coffee. Fully fenced in back yard perfect for enjoying your outdoor garden. Plenty of room for a pool! Double entry gate, bring your boat, RV, or trailer. Security system with cameras stay with property. Quiet location, close to Tradition and St Lucie West, shopping and dining. Turnpike and I95 nearby for easy commutes.
